Check `state.GetRejectCode() == REJECT_DUPLICATE`? See [this](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blame/master/src/validation.cpp#L476).

Also, IMO this is prettier:
```cpp
if (state.IsValid()) {
    ...
} else if (state.GetRejectCode() == REJECT_DUPLICATE) {
    ...
} else {
    ...
}
